@SpaceIDProtocol .bnb 域名预注册模式最新改动：

▪️ 可看到愿望清单中相同域名的提交人数，并支持二次修改（竞拍信心不足就趁早换）

▪️ 竞拍失败者可在第四阶段“先到先得” 模式下继续注册等量域名（避免因竞拍失败而浪费名额）

▪️ 拍卖产生的所有额外利润将以 $BNB 形式重新分配给所有参与用户

Example for point 3: if aaa.bnb is auctioned for $500, then the additional profit is 500-390=110. The $110 USD would be distributed in BNB to all users who participated in the pre-registration phase. The redistribution will be based on the amount of domains registered on a wallet

3. To further stress that our only aim of the auction mechanism is to have a fair launch, we will be redistributing ALL the additional profits from the auctions during the pre-registration phase back to the domain holders.

2. Those that lost the domain name auction will be able to register domains on 'First Come First Serve' (FCFS) model in the newly created Phase 4. Example: if you lost 5 domain auctions in Phase 2, you'll be able to register 5 domains in Phase 4.

1. You will be able to see the number of users who added the same domain name into the Wishlist. You'll also be able to change your Wishlist domains until the end of Phase I. This will help you know how many other users you are competing against for that specific domain name.
